<h2>Welcome to the Estonian e-Business Register API Demo</h2>

<p>This interactive demo application showcases the <strong>ee_e_business_register</strong> Ruby gem - a clean & simple interface to the Estonian e-Business Register API following the KISS principle.</p>

<div class="info">
  <strong>ℹ️ Note:</strong> You need valid API credentials to use this demo. Configure them in your environment variables or <code>.env</code> file.
</div>

<h3>Available API Endpoints</h3>

<div class="grid">
  <a href="/company/find" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>🔍 Find Company</h3>
    <p>Look up a specific company by its 8-digit registry code. Returns basic company information including name, status, and address.</p>
  </a>
  
  <a href="/company/detailed" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>📋 Detailed Company Data</h3>
    <p>Get comprehensive company information including business activities, personnel, capital, and registration details.</p>
  </a>
  
  <a href="/documents" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>📄 Company Documents</h3>
    <p>Retrieve a list of documents filed by a company with the Estonian Business Register.</p>
  </a>
  
  <a href="/reports/annual" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>📊 Annual Reports List</h3>
    <p>Get a list of all annual reports filed by a company, with submission dates and report types.</p>
  </a>
  
  <a href="/reports/data" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>💰 Annual Report Data</h3>
    <p>Access detailed financial data from annual reports including balance sheet, income statement, and cash flow.</p>
  </a>
  
  <a href="/representation" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>👥 Representatives</h3>
    <p>View who has the right to represent the company, including board members and authorized signatories.</p>
  </a>
  
  <a href="/beneficial_owners" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>💼 Beneficial Owners</h3>
    <p>Access beneficial ownership information for compliance and transparency requirements.</p>
  </a>
  
  <a href="/classifiers" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>📋 Classifiers</h3>
    <p>Access reference data including legal forms, company statuses, regions, and other classification systems.</p>
  </a>
  
  <a href="/health" class="endpoint-card">
    <h3>💚 API Health & Status</h3>
    <p>Check if the Estonian e-Business Register API is accessible and responding correctly.</p>
  </a>
</div>

